    "For instance, AthenaTest [135] employed a two-stage pre-training strategy.",
    "The model was first trained on a large English text corpus, followed by training on Java source code to learn its specific syntax and structure.",
    "RQ1 Key InsightDominance of Prompt Engineering and the Decisive Role of Iterative Refinement: Although pre-training and fine-tuning provide the necessary model foundation, advanced prompt engineering (accounting for 89%) has emerged as the most influential deployment paradigm.",
    "In particular, placing LLMs within a \"Generate-Validate-Repair\" iterative loop has become the de facto standard for addressing the low usability of raw LLM outputs.",
    "This mechanism can boost test pass rates from under 30% to over 70%, yielding marginal benefits that far surpass those of mere model parameter adjustments."
